{"tid":161610,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點同男朋友講結婚?","createTime":"2017-03-18T16:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T16:21:00.000Z","uid":63266,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1cc158a722b36e7a2d1570db83e13e409e5bd85","tid":161610,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"一齊咗兩年 <br />\n認定咗係大家  感情穩定<br />\n見過晒大家屋企人<br />\n有時會去吓家庭聚會<br />\n<br />\n初初有提起過想27歲就結婚<br />\n男朋友都ok<br />\n個時佢仲話想快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲有幾個月就grad 出黎做嘢<br />\n男朋友一年前就出黎做嘢  收入穩定<br />\n我仲有4年就27 <br />\n<br />\n我個人較為有計劃 <br />\n由其係啲大事上面<br />\n所以想好好地同男朋友傾下呢4年點儲錢個啲<br />\n因為我知到時結婚會用唔少錢<br />\n住個方面就唔洗擔心  但仲有其他洗費<br />\n註冊  搵律師  擺酒(未知)  渡蜜月 等等<br />\n想傾下點一齊儲錢<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚我咁會俾佢壓力<br />\n但係我又好想可以早啲計劃好<br />\n同埋起碼知大家對結婚各項洗費個啲點睇<br />\n而儲錢呢啲嘢愈早愈好<br />\n<br />\n但應該點開口同男朋友講好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a118ead8d293b7896328dffcd01bd9231b6a3f","tid":161610,"uid":20270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊咗兩年 <br />\n認定咗係大家  感情穩定<br />\n見過晒大家屋企人<br />\n有時會去吓家庭聚會<br />\n<br />\n初初有提起過想27歲就結婚<br />\n男朋友都ok<br />\n個時佢仲話想快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲有幾個月就grad 出黎做嘢<br />\n男朋友一年前就出黎做嘢  收入穩定<br />\n我仲有4年就27 <br />\n<br />\n我個人較為有計劃 <br />\n由其係啲大事上面<br />\n所以想好好地同男朋友傾下呢4年點儲錢個啲<br />\n因為我知到時結婚會用唔少錢<br />\n住個方面就唔洗擔心  但仲有其他洗費<br />\n註冊  搵律師  擺酒(未知)  渡蜜月 等等<br />\n想傾下點一齊儲錢<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚我咁會俾佢壓力<br />\n但係我又好想可以早啲計劃好<br />\n同埋起碼知大家對結婚各項洗費個啲點睇<br />\n而儲錢呢啲嘢愈早愈好<br />\n<br />\n但應該點開口同男朋友講好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果樓已解決 照直講駛儲幾多"},{"pid":"9fdd47cb6ed457ddceb51c2530add88f5d26dd3e","tid":161610,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"本身有冇買樓/供樓?"},{"pid":"b5ce2c1b5d6d3830bb70b27b93685ae5c6da99e1","tid":161610,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"搵個好時機<br />\n問下佢 睇下有咩反應先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔係狂問我諗都唔會算逼佢既"},{"pid":"ffe9ed4a0702f42697ac304dbb392a2c320e96ce","tid":161610,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"未做野無收入就諗結婚 佢好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ec624cb389d640050afb2d636781523eaf598d","tid":161610,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:09:08.000Z","msg":"其實如果你男友真係愛你既話，你主動照直同佢講想同佢結婚，佢應該都會好開心，之後咪大家認真傾下，利申死毒撚尻up"},{"pid":"4c0db2fc09ded01a7f1b8a8d572561ba50257744","tid":161610,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"我兩個月冇黎m"},{"pid":"15b0e5812e6629355bcc973810f701e2d8cf1293","tid":161610,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:16:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一齊咗兩年 <br />\n認定咗係大家  感情穩定<br />\n見過晒大家屋企人<br />\n有時會去吓家庭聚會<br />\n<br />\n初初有提起過想27歲就結婚<br />\n男朋友都ok<br />\n個時佢仲話想快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲有幾個月就grad 出黎做嘢<br />\n男朋友一年前就出黎做嘢  收入穩定<br />\n我仲有4年就27 <br />\n<br />\n我個人較為有計劃 <br />\n由其係啲大事上面<br />\n所以想好好地同男朋友傾下呢4年點儲錢個啲<br />\n因為我知到時結婚會用唔少錢<br />\n住個方面就唔洗擔心  但仲有其他洗費<br />\n註冊  搵律師  擺酒(未知)  渡蜜月 等等<br />\n想傾下點一齊儲錢<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚我咁會俾佢壓力<br />\n但係我又好想可以早啲計劃好<br />\n同埋起碼知大家對結婚各項洗費個啲點睇<br />\n而儲錢呢啲嘢愈早愈好<br />\n<br />\n但應該點開口同男朋友講好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果樓已解決 照直講駛儲幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好驚我照直講會俾壓力佢<br />\n我知男人對呢啲好似好敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一啲壓力都唔想俾佢"},{"pid":"286f2ca09006c4a7323b9e55f07dcf957393ee57","tid":161610,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身有冇買樓/供樓?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢本身有樓"},{"pid":"253d3f3c3c479ebc079a4bea5ea4374cc1455aa5","tid":161610,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵個好時機<br />\n問下佢 睇下有咩反應先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔係狂問我諗都唔會算逼佢既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點為之好時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同唔知開口點講"},{"pid":"61de7229b5d080f2a1cd791ade4ed6fbeb6cb250","tid":161610,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未做野無收入就諗結婚 佢好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係由細到大都好有計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀大學錢都係中三就開始儲"},{"pid":"9168ebef20ff56a1011c6d1330956235e5bd5d71","tid":161610,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:18:59.000Z","msg":"重有成4年，你唔怕中途分手 ？"},{"pid":"399783f89187b3d001714ef21bce9f104557eb3b","tid":161610,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我兩個月冇黎m</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做足安全措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藥+套"},{"pid":"6a4d99cedd7f26125786489a8562a44b50dfd966","tid":161610,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實如果你男友真係愛你既話，你主動照直同佢講想同佢結婚，佢應該都會好開心，之後咪大家認真傾下，利申死毒撚尻up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係應該點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身都唔係好識開口表達自己嘅人<br />\n有諗過text佢傾<br />\n但呢啲事好似親口好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2809e593bb3bc3d3e64c8acf8e9ea5d417da4d","tid":161610,"uid":63266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重有成4年，你唔怕中途分手 ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕<br />\n對大家好有信心<br />\n好想一直行落去<br />\n只係我想計劃好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0941f1292f33185a6b7aa3724a916a679c76aa01","tid":161610,"uid":72967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"早4年計劃又真係太早 睇定d先 男女關係好化學"},{"pid":"e4f4b405f093fafa41d0755f1930484c05d71be3","tid":161610,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"三潘市幫到你地， 個邊係合法既"},{"pid":"aa305840f49adf57afe7530ccdc6ea85dc8083d1","tid":161610,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d905e42f25f2098e68541a8c34fe0329938ade4","tid":161610,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d61124c184cc28445d47f6e99119540b4d11433","tid":161610,"uid":72967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本身有冇買樓/供樓?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢本身有樓</blockquote><br />\n唔怪得咁心急啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我男友冇樓 大家都2x歲 我都成日催佢結婚 主要係認定佢係結婚對象 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc899572dfd781da124238b68eb3429f3fad308e","tid":161610,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"4年駛鬼咁快講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你自己慣咗預早計劃唔代表人地一定要跟你個步伐，仲有4年先27，呢4年會有好多變數，尤其是出嚟工作之後更加多未知數發生，你咁快提呢樣野，好容易令對方覺得你chur住佢。"},{"pid":"d9be5987964d816f6b24738e6037b2b2eb5b05b0","tid":161610,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c21c742adc5ce51a7cfa1d4c7d8fda94ea7c8c5","tid":161610,"uid":35178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"原來男友有樓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw你男友有樓，即係錢銀唔緊張啦，結婚最多用4-50萬正常咁搞，駛咩儲啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你早四年叫男友Plan定反而比壓力佢，到時你出左黎做野個心態可能又唔同呢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdf8d7a741ce89656529e753e717014e980c26e","tid":161610,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"伙記埋單"},{"pid":"c9d78ee8112690cdd035c7b9eefd4bb3ea0b85b3","tid":161610,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"直接講 我想27結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}